\c 7
\nb
\v 1 Njalo abantu beKiriyathi-Jeyarimi beza\x + 6.21.\x*, benyusa umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*, bawungenisa endlini kaAbinadaba phezu kwaloloqaqa, bangcwelisa uEleyazare indodana yakhe ukuthi agcine umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2 Sam. 6.3.\x*.
\s USamuweli wahlulela uIsrayeli
\p
\v 2 Kwasekusithi kusukela ngosuku umtshokotsho uhlala eKiriyathi-Jeyarimi, insuku zanda; ngoba kwaba yiminyaka engamatshumi amabili; lendlu yonke yakoIsrayeli yakhala ilandela iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 3 USamuweli wasekhuluma endlini yonke kaIsrayeli esithi: Uba libuyela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngenhliziyo yenu yonke\x + Isa. 55.7. Hos. 6.1. Dute. 30.2-10. 1 Kho. 8.48. Jow. 2.12.\x*, susani onkulunkulu bezizweni phakathi kwenu\x + Hlu. 10.16.\x* laboAshitarothi\x + Hlu. 2.13.\x*, liqondise inhliziyo yenu eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 2 Lan. 19.3. 30.19. Ezra 7.10. Jobe 11.13. Hlab. 78.8.\x*, likhonze yona yodwa, ngakho izalophula esandleni samaFilisti\x + Dute. 6.13. 10.20. 13.4. Mat. 4.10. Luka 4.8.\x*.
\v 4 Ngakho abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesusa oBhali laboAshitarothi, bakhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* yodwa\x + Hlu. 2.13.\x*.
\p
\v 5 USamuweli wasesithi: Buthanisani uIsrayeli wonke eMizipa\x + Josh. 18.26.\x*; njalo ngizalikhulekela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 7.9. Gen. 20.7.\x*.
\v 6 Basebebuthana eMizipa, bakha amanzi, bawathela phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2 Sam. 14.14.\x*, bazila ukudla mhlalokho\x + 28.20. 31.13. Hlu. 20.26. Neh. 9.1. Dan. 9.3,4,5. Jow. 2.12.\x*, bathi lapho: Sonile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hlu. 10.10. 1 Kho. 8.47.\x*. USamuweli wasesahlulela abantwana bakoIsrayeli eMizipa.
\p
\v 7 Kwathi amaFilisti esezwile ukuthi abantwana bakoIsrayeli babuthene eMizipa, iziphathamandla zamaFilisti zenyuka zamelana loIsrayeli. Abantwana bakoIsrayeli sebekuzwile bawesaba amaFilisti.
\v 8 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesithi kuSamuweli: Ungathuli ukusikhalela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wethu ukuze asisindise esandleni samaFilisti\x + Eks. 14.14. 2 Kho. 19.4. Isa. 37.4.\x*.
\v 9 USamuweli wasethatha iwundlu elimunyayo, walinikela lonke eN\nd kosi\nd*ni laba ngumnikelo otshiswayo. USamuweli wakhalela uIsrayeli eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, iN\nd kosi\nd* yasimphendula\x + Hlab. 99.6. Jer. 15.1.\x*.
\v 10 Kwathi uSamuweli esanikela umnikelo wokutshiswa, amaFilisti asondela empini loIsrayeli; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yaduma ngelizwi elikhulu phezu kwamaFilisti ngalolosuku\x + 2.10. Hlab. 18.13. 2 Sam. 22.14,15.\x*, yawachithachitha, asetshaywa phambi kukaIsrayeli\x + Josh. 10.10. Hlu. 5.20.\x*.
\v 11 Amadoda akoIsrayeli asephuma eMizipa axotshana lamaFilisti, awatshaya, kwaze kwaba ngaphansi kweBetikari.
\v 12 USamuweli wasethatha ilitshe, wa\add li\add*misa phakathi kweMizipa leSheni, wabiza ibizo lalo iEbeni-Ezeri\x + Gen. 28.18. 31.45. 35.14. Josh. 4.9. 24.26.\x*, wathi: Kuze kube khathesi iN\nd kosi\nd* isisizile\x + Nani 14.19.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Ngakho amaFilisti ehliselwa phansi\x + Hlu. 13.1.\x*, kawabe esaphinda ukungena emngceleni wakoIsrayeli\x + 13.5.\x*. Njalo isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* samelana lamaFilisti zonke izinsuku zikaSamuweli\x + 5.9.\x*.
\v 14 Imizi amaFilisti ayeyithethe-ke koIsrayeli yabuyiselwa kuIsrayeli kusukela eEkhironi\x + Josh. 15.11.\x* kuze kufike eGathi\x + 17.4.\x*; lomngcele wayo uIsrayeli wawukhulula esandleni samaFilisti. Njalo kwaba lokuthula phakathi kukaIsrayeli lamaAmori\x + Gen. 15.16.\x*.
\p
\v 15 USamuweli wasesahlulela uIsrayeli insuku zonke zempilo yakhe\x + 7.6. 12.11. 25.1.\x*.
\v 16 Wahamba iminyaka ngeminyaka wabhoda eBhetheli\x + Josh. 16.2.\x*, leGiligali\x + Josh. 5.9.\x*, leMizipa\x + Josh. 18.26.\x*; wahlulela uIsrayeli kuzo zonke lezozindawo.
\v 17 Lokubuyela kwakhe kwakuyikuya eRama\x + 1.19.\x*, ngoba indlu yakhe yayilapho; wahlulela uIsrayeli khona, wayakhela lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi\x + 7.9. 14.35. Hlu. 21.4.\x*.